---
const today = new Date();
---
<footer>
	<div class="footer-grid">
		<div class="footer-brand">
			<img src="https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663793082257/ogPOsdkRxADEqSrf.png" alt="A-Zent" class="logo-img" />
			<p>沖縄の中小企業・個人事業主に<br />IT導入・DX支援・ホームページ制作で<br />寄り添うITパートナーです。</p>
			<div class="footer-contact">
				<p><strong>A-Zent（アゼント）</strong></p>
				<p>〒903-0802 那覇市首里大名町2-2-102</p>
				<p><a href="tel:09087026434">📞 090-8702-6434</a></p>
				<p><a href="mailto:info@a-zent.com">✉ info@a-zent.com</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-nav">
			<h5>Menu</h5>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/">ホーム</a></li>
				<li><a href="/about">会社案内</a></li>
				<li><a href="/blog">ブログ</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-bottom">
		&copy; {today.getFullYear()} A-Zent. All rights reserved. | 〒903-0802 那覇市首里大名町2-2-102
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		background: #f5f5f5;
		color: #3D3A36;
		padding: 56px 40px 32px;
		border-top: 1px solid #eee;
		text-align: left;
	}
	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
		gap: 60px;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto 40px;
	}
	.logo-img {
		height: 36px;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}
	.footer-brand p {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}
	.footer-contact {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
	.footer-contact a {
		color: #E8302A;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.footer-nav h5 {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		color: #1A1816;
	}
	.footer-nav ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}
	.footer-nav li {
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}
	.footer-nav a {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: #3D3A36;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
		padding-top: 20px;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		text-align: center;
		opacity: 0.6;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 32px;
		}
		footer {
			padding: 40px 20px 24px;
		}
	}
</style>
